_sText:
This is V1 of my space area. I have been thinking that I might take this farther and make a GG map out of it.

Thought I would also throw it up here to let anybody else use it.

Uses: Lights, Props, Smoke, Sparks, Background Sound (Machinery Humming), Cables/Ropes, Vertex Manipulation. 

Has been properly NoDraw'd and Func_Detailed for optimization.

Left the textures for you guys to do, I don't want to do it all. Some sexy custom space textures will look good here.

Have fun with it guys.

Please Download/Asses it for me, its the only way I will learn....
